{"tid":10791,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA 17 Ultimate Team 討論區 (1) 重新開此","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T05:46:25.000Z","uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe6888b82b7857b8e5561d982f15df5723bfb13","tid":10791,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PG1X7c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPG1X7c4.jpg&h=11fcd71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWeb App: <a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app/show-off\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Fweb-app%2Fshow-off&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=a82643b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/web-app/show-off</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入FIFA17 Ultimate Team討論區(ps3/ps4 ,xbox/xbox 1,pc) <br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知既野先問，好多你想知既野都係第一版！拜託曬！<br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT 17 web app: <a href=\"http://www.ea.com/soccer/fifa-ultimate-team\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ea.com%2Fsoccer%2Ffifa-ultimate-team&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3f29d2f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ea.com/soccer/fifa-ultimate-team</a> <br />\n<br />\n球員資料database: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.futhead.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.futhead.com&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=de8dde30\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.futhead.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.futwiz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.futwiz.com&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=46950f9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.futwiz.com</a><br />\n<br />\nFUT DATABASE <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easports.com%2Ffifa%2Fultimate-team%2Ffut%2Fdatabase&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=eb4e5fb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.easports.com/fifa/ultimate-team/fut/database</a>"},{"pid":"5fda36537097820427665a87ada61e6aaf4adbed","tid":10791,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A <br />\n<br />\n1.點樣可以contract 50%? <br />\n答:閃卡教練會加contract%, 金 3%銀 2%銅 1%, 普通金 1%, 總之最多50%, <br />\n買完個教練就咁store in club就可以加約。 <br />\n<br />\n2.係咪有金包送架? <br />\n答:係 game入面有張卡，其中一條係金包code <br />\n如果有, 係PS Store入面入code, 每星期就可以拎一包金包，記住唔係一次過拎晒 <br />\n<br />\n3. 點賺錢? <br />\n答:踏實d, 打杯打比賽, 要快手就去淘寶課金, 切記今年EA&rdquo; 話&rdquo; 會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負 <br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。 <br />\n另外要留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500 <br />\n<br />\n4. 咩係chemistry? <br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力 <br />\n<br />\n5. 咁點加chemistry呀? <br />\n答:位置、球員之間既連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。 <br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係綠色連線? <br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線 <br />\n有3個原素 <br />\na.國籍 b.聯賽 c.球隊 <br />\n符合兩樣就夠, 咁樣有綠色連線 <br />\n一樣的話都有橙色 <br />\n<br />\n7. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色? <br />\n答:每星期三晚2點am都會有新既TOTW (team of the week) <br />\n出既人會有張加強版既黑色卡，又叫IF (in form) <br />\nNIF (not in form)係指有出過IF既人既普通版 <br />\n黑卡因為多數只會出一個星期唔會再出，所以相當保值 <br />\n<br />\n8. 咩係happy hour? 點解有時會有d限數量既pack? <br />\n答:EA有時會出promo pack，如15,000 coins既premium jumbo pack <br />\n有時一星期會有一兩個鐘既happy hour(唔知幾時先再有)，同有special promo pack之類，呢個係唔定時，視乎係咩種類既pack，可以抽5次或者10次，最貴既100K pack (24個全閃金球員)就只限抽一次 <br />\n要留意EASPORTSFIFA既twitter <br />\n<br />\n9.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐? <br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style <br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴(假設chemistry 10), 唔代表果項能力 1 <br />\nchemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去 <br />\n<br />\n10: 隻Game 有無 handicap? 咩係handicap <br />\n答: 有handicap已經係公開嘅秘密,而Handicap會令你經常有著數, 例如55波爭贏, 射門入球率大增 <br />\n而點先會令佢出現, 通常d人會透過壓星(壓Rating) 去令佢出現 <br />\n<br />\n11: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀? <br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, 分H-high, M-mehim, L-low <br />\nH/H就則係個球員atk同def work rate都係high"},{"pid":"9019a92255c662faa454a68453d1ba3675b74cf0","tid":10791,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046d42073bfdd1e591ab7d38935fe71b217eb7bb","tid":10791,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd753494f2365d00798a0d71cdf32684c5b8f46e","tid":10791,"uid":16088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39fb8578963b91313828fa41add685d38008ac9","tid":10791,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"telegram 啲人會唔會返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20538dd743b12362f84b262128b68bed707b7ad","tid":10791,"uid":40607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"好靜&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544d4792d8d106094cac74e3d37ca6392baee1ab","tid":10791,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"新手應該點做<br />\n淨係買合約都買到窮"},{"pid":"1be5b46f0b8dda0e1ba925559284c45296e65bad","tid":10791,"uid":30871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"放450k ps4 coins<br />\nPM 留whatsapp"},{"pid":"98dec1cd185bd08942fb8a81c14bba61557de797","tid":10791,"uid":59534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"送既金包其實係咪唔會中好野..."}